<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="lt">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Pasiūlymas nerastas | LedPro</title>
  <link href="https://fonts.cdnfonts.com/css/samsung-sans-4" rel="stylesheet">
  <style>
    * { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }
    body {
      font-family: 'Samsung Sans', sans-serif;
      background: #fafaf9;
      color: #1c1917;
      min-height: 100vh;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      padding: 2rem;
    }
    .content { text-align: center; }
    h1 { font-size: 1.5rem; margin-bottom: 0.5rem; }
    p { color: #78716c; margin-bottom: 1.5rem; }
    a { color: #0f766e; text-decoration: none; }
    a:hover { text-decoration: underline; }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="content">
    <h1>Pasiūlymas nerastas</h1>
    <p>Pasiūlymas „<%= slug %>“ neegzistuoja arba buvo pašalintas.</p>
    <a href="/">Grįžti į pradžią</a>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
